  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "folder 49 - 096\nOnce he chooses correctly in the Key situation the Books are closed on him. Adjudication is rendered, & secular time for him ends. This is an existential choice, not theoretical, & may well involve his very physical existence; he stakes _everything_. or it could be an ostensibly small matter, or perhaps a series of actions. It resembles the Pythagorean \"Y.\" Since Satan really rules this world it is very likely that te person will have to split with the world, but not necessarily.",
